        "auditory": "I hear a controlled inhale, then a slow exhale-breathing that sounds like someone taking command of themselves.",
        "olfactory": "I smell a clean spike of adrenaline-sweat, sharp but controlled.",
        "tactile": "Someone's body goes rigid for a beat, then steadies-tension reorganizing into readiness instead of panic."
